| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1310 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 565a884d-15f8-5a61-bcbc-43d58e02bb37"
